# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# blankand0 environment variables
# Copy to .env.local for local dev, or set these in the Vercel project settings.
# Nothing here is required to build or play — only the global leaderboard needs it.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Global leaderboard storage — Vercel KV / Upstash Redis (REST API).
# OPTIONAL: without these, the leaderboard still works but uses an in-memory
# store that resets on every serverless cold start (i.e. not a real global board).
# In the Vercel dashboard: Storage -> create a KV / Upstash store and connect it
# to this project; these two vars are injected automatically. Copy them here for
# local development if you want to test persistence.
KV_REST_API_URL=
KV_REST_API_TOKEN=
